---
# Modify default clang-tidy settings for test code.
# * GTEST macros have a lot of conditionals that means even trivial
#   tests will exceed the cognitive complexity limit.
# * Using endl is fine in test code.
Checks: >-
  -readability-function-cognitive-complexity,
  -performance-avoid-endl
InheritParentConfig: true
...
